{"tid":2183212,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–建構人造腸道厚膜的藥物","createTime":"2020-08-31T20:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T02:56:40.000Z","uid":38861,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6bfe4517c9626959ac5f3494f032289eb5fee947","tid":2183212,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T20:31:53.000Z","msg":"腸道是人體吸收葡萄糖的主要地方，亦是消化乳糖酵素(Lactase）的聚居地。<br />\n缺乏Lactase的人並不建議進食含有乳糖的產品，否則會釀起肚痾、腹痛、作嘔等症狀，學名為Lactose Intolerance。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8oFrrm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8oFrrm.jpg&h=d74eb754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同時，腸道亦是寄生蟲的蝸居，飲用不乾淨水的話有機會讓血吸蟲寄生在腸道之中，引起血吸蟲病（Schistosomiasis)，為全球第二大僅次於瘧疾(Malaria)的寄生蟲病。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）近日，有科學家發表文章（Ref1)，他們研發出一款口服藥物，主要利用豬隻作為動物模型，證實豬隻吞下藥物後的12分鐘會腸道形成厚膜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMzpS6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMzpS6p.jpg&h=640d1302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此厚膜不會在其他器官上形成，而在24小時後厚膜亦會自然脫落，排出體外。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）根據口服藥物的配方不同，厚膜的特性亦能隨之轉變。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mErjGZO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmErjGZO.jpg&h=df96bfb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n厚膜可配載消化乳糖酵素(Lactase)，對比沒有厚膜，能增強20倍酵素的能力，可消除Lactose Intolerance的問題。<br />\n<br />\n而增強厚膜密度的話，亦可減少腸道吸收葡萄糖七成能力，這特點尤其受益於糖尿病人，能大幅度阻上血糖飄升。<br />\n<br />\n另外，厚膜亦可配載殺寄生蟲藥(Praziquantel)，增加藥物滯留在腸道的時間，更有效率殺滅寄生蟲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）最為振奮的是，此方法在人類腸道組織亦見效，而且藥物對各種實驗室人體細胞亦無呈現有害效果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bxa8AjR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxa8AjR.jpg&h=9bf6314c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老鼠服用藥物28日後，體重血壓等一切正常。<br />\n<br />\n若然此藥物能進一步在人類進行試驗的話，確立藥物運作正常及不會帶來任何副作用或安全問題的話，絕對大有潛質會成為治理糖尿病的新一代藥物。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=f304b6df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=b700f7a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://stm.sciencemag.org/content/12/558/eabc0441\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstm.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F12%2F558%2Feabc0441&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=ca22cb13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stm.sciencemag.org/content/12/558/eabc0441</a>"},{"pid":"f21b8a536d1ef46c52ccc7623df7c9507b89059d","tid":2183212,"uid":358248,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T20:55:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7da7f4de35945224ad310f113ab92bd3c2a8abdd","tid":2183212,"uid":280648,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T23:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飲唔到奶嘅人終於可以享受飲奶嘅樂趣<b